snippet.title: GCLIFE Live Stream
snippet.description:
Generation Church, Pastors Josh and Amber Clark, in Goldsboro, NC.

Discover your purpose and be encourage in your faith today in this life-changing message from the Word of God.  Thanks for joining us!

STAY CONNECTED 
Stay updated with the latest news from Generation Church at http://www.facebook.com/generationgoldsboro.  You can also download the Generation Church app for Apple and Android devices.  Text GCLIFEAPP to 77977 and enable push notifications. 

PRAYER REQUESTS
If you need prayer or have any updates for us, please fill out an online RED CARD, our weekly prayer card and point-of-contact.  We love to hear from you!  You can fill it out now: https://form.jotform.com/200807389483059

SUPPORT COVID-19 RESPONSE AND CHURCH MINISTRIES
Your financial support to Generation Church help support all of our ministries.  Your generosity has enables us to provide local coronavirus relief, including additional Food Bank and outreaches to local prisons! Your gift helps meet immediate needs in your community and around the world and helps us spread the Good News of Jesus Christ to people everywhere: https://pushpay.com/g/gcgoldsboro

DRIVE-IN SUNDAYS
In addition to in-person services at  9:30 and 11am, if you are at-risk and prefer not to come inside, you can listen live in our church parking lot. Tune your radio to 100.1 FM and join in!

NEXT STEPS 
Have you made a decision to follow Jesus? Interested in being Baptized? You may be wondering what’s next on your journey. We want to help! Fill out a RED CARD and let us help you in your walk with God: https://form.jotform.com/200807389483059

ABOUT GENERATION CHURCH 
Wherever you are in life, you have a purpose. We want you to help you discover your God-given purpose in life.  Join us weekly in person or online!  You can learn more about us at www.gc.life or download the Generation Church app available on the App Store or Google Play.  You can also text GCLIFEAPP to 77977.

FIND US ON SOCIAL MEDIA 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/generationgoldsboro
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/generation.church
Podcast: https://goldsborofirst.podbean.com/

CONNECT WITH PASTOR JOSH
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/pastorjoshclark 
Email: jc@gc.life
